'''''The Crawl''''' is an album by pianist [[Mickey Tucker]] which was recorded in 1979 and released on the [[Muse Records|Muse]] label.<ref>[http://www.jazzdiscography.com/Labels/muse.htm Muse Records discography] accessed May 2, 2014</ref>
==Reception==
{{Album ratings
| rev1 = ''[[Allmusic]]''
| rev1Score = {{rating|3|5}}<ref name="Allmusic"/> 
| rev2 = ''[[The Rolling Stone Jazz Record Guide]]''
