The [[Allmusic]] review awarded the album 3 stars stating "Tucker plays decent piano and outstanding organ, and it's the organ solos and accompaniment that generate the infrequent sparks".<ref name="Allmusic">Wynn, R., [http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-crawl-mw0000864601 Allmusic listing], accessed May 2, 2014</ref> 
== Track listing ==
''All compositions by Mickey Tucker except as indicated''
