# "It Could Be, If It Was, But It Ain't" - 7:17  
# "Just a Thought for Love" - 4:05  
# "June Bug, June Bug; Where You Fly?" - 6:05  
# "Pisces Brothers" ([[Roy Brooks]]) - 8:35  
# "Marcus Tiberius and the Gladiator" - 4:02  

